Title: Rescuing Your 2023 Goals
Description:
It may feel like it's time to write off your 2023 goals, but Michael and Megan are here to tell you how you can make the most out of the rest of the year. They share some reasons why we find ourselves adrift from our goals and then provide a five-step framework to help you finish out the year strong.
